OL,3,CBreast cancer patient faces race
OL,4,Cagainst time to access life-extending
OL,5,Cdrug
OL,7,FA breast cancer patient from Greater
OL,8,FManchester says she's devastated and
OL,9,Fangry that a drug that she believes
OL,10,Fcould extend her life is still not
OL,11,Favailable on the NHS in England.
OL,13,FSarah Barchetti, who has been living
OL,14,Fwith secondary breast cancer for seven
OL,15,Fyears, has been treated at The
OL,16,FChristie hospital in Manchester
OL,17,Fthroughout her illness. But now, as
OL,18,FNHS treatment options dwindle, Sarah
OL,19,Fhas turned to fundraising for private
OL,20,Fcare.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
