OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784053123
OL,3,CBreast cancer patient faces race
OL,4,Cagainst time to access life-extending
OL,5,Cdrug
OL,7,FSarah said: "It blew our world apart,"
OL,8,Frecalling her diagnosis in 2019.
OL,10,FShe added: "I've lived with it now for
OL,11,Fseven years. I'm eternally grateful to
OL,12,FThe Christie, but we've come to a
OL,13,Fpoint now where they can't offer me
OL,14,Fanything else under the NHS. My team
OL,15,Fare as frustrated as I am."
OL,17,FSarah believes the drug Enhertu could
OL,18,Fhelp her, but while it is available to
OL,19,FNHS patients with HER2-low metastatic
OL,20,Fbreast cancer in Scotland, it is not
OL,21,Fyet offered in England.
OL,26,@oD@MOUoD@fO]rD@LOUwD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
