CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784053123
OL,3,CBreast cancer patient faces race
OL,4,Cagainst time to access life-extending
OL,5,Cdrug
OL,7,FNICE, the body that assesses and
OL,8,Frecommends treatments, did not approve
OL,9,Fthe drug in 2024, citing concerns over
OL,10,Fcost-effectiveness at the
OL,11,Fmanufacturer's price.
OL,13,FWith time running out, Sarah and her
OL,14,Fhusband Martin have set about raising
OL,15,Ffunds for private treatment.
OL,17,FMartin said: "Our hands have been
OL,18,Fforced. The fees are astronomical, and
OL,19,Fit's really time sensitive.
OL,26,@yD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784053123
OL,3,CBreast cancer patient faces race
OL,4,Cagainst time to access life-extending
OL,5,Cdrug
OL,7,F"So we've had to resort to this. The
OL,8,Fresponse of friends, family,
OL,9,Fstrangers, local businesses`it's been
OL,10,Ffantastic in such a short space of
OL,11,Ftime."
OL,13,FIn just two weeks, the family has
OL,14,Fraised nearly a quarter of the money
OL,15,Fthey need, but the target is still a
OL,16,Flong way off.
OL,18,FSarah said: "We're constantly trying
OL,19,Fto think of new ideas to raise funds,"
OL,26,@sD@FO]zD@MOU{D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
