CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784053123
OL,3,CBreast cancer patient faces race
OL,4,Cagainst time to access life-extending
OL,5,Cdrug
OL,7,FNICE says discussions with the drug
OL,8,Fmanufacturer have resumed, following
OL,9,Fthe new US-UK trade deal announced in
OL,10,FDecember 2025, and is willing to
OL,11,Freview its guidance if a new
OL,12,Fcommercial offer is made.
OL,14,FBut for Sarah and Martin, any decision
OL,15,Fcannot come soon enough.
OL,17,FMartin added: "We just want to focus
OL,18,Fon Sarah and us as a family, and not
OL,19,Fhave to worry about costs and things
OL,20,Flike that,"
OL,26,@yD@OOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
