PN,36706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784053123
OL,3,CBreast cancer patient faces race
OL,4,Cagainst time to access life-extending
OL,5,Cdrug
OL,7,FA NICE spokesperson said: "Enhertu for
OL,8,FHER2-low metastatic breast cancer is
OL,9,Fthe only breast cancer treatment NICE
OL,10,Fhas been unable to recommend in the
OL,11,Flast eight years.
OL,13,F"In 2024, we concluded that, at the
OL,14,Fprice offered, the treatment was not
OL,15,Fcost effective. However, following the
OL,16,FUS-UK trade deal, NICE is now applying
OL,17,Fa new, higher threshold for cost-
OL,18,Feffectiveness decisions.
OL,26,@oD@[OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
