FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784053123
OL,3,CBreast cancer patient faces race
OL,4,Cagainst time to access life-extending
OL,5,Cdrug
OL,7,F"Discussions have resumed with the aim
OL,8,Fof reaching a commercial agreement. We
OL,9,Fstand ready to review our guidance
OL,10,Fshould new evidence or a new offer be
OL,11,Fput forward."
OL,13,FFor now, Sarah and her family continue
OL,14,Ftheir fight, not just for her own
OL,15,Ffuture, but to highlight the urgent
OL,16,Fneed for access to life-extending
OL,17,Ftreatments for others in her position.
OL,19,FThose wishing to support Sarah's
OL,20,Fcampaign can donate via her GoFundMe
OL,21,Fpage.
OL,26,@sD@MO]
